<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.10.2">
<l>perunīrum viṇṇum malaiyu mulakēḻum</l>
<l>orutārā niṉṉu ḷoṭukkiya niṉṉaiyallāl</l>
<l>varutēvar maṟṟuḷa reṉṟeṉ maṉattiṟaiyum</l>
<l>karutēṉnāṉ kaṇṇa purattuṟai yammāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Except for you who compressed within yourself the vast waters,</l>
<l>Heavens, mountains, and seven worlds, as [if] a garland,</l>
<l>I do not imagine in my mind for even a second</l>
<l>That there are other gods who appear [incarnate],</l>
<l rend="indent">lord who dwells in Kaṇṇapuram.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
